{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_012QUdtWMUvBaNy4anA5ufW4","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The migration is complete. Here is the full report:\n\n---\n\n### Migration Summary\n\n- **Frameworks:** Jakarta EE 10 (Open Liberty) -> Spring Boot 3.2.5 (Embedded Tomcat)\n- **High-level actions:** Replaced EJB with Spring Services, JSF with Thymeleaf, Open Liberty with embedded Tomcat, added REST API, created 15 smoke tests\n- **Overall outcome:** Success - all 15 smoke tests pass, application builds, runs, and functions correctly\n\n### File Tree\n\n```\nModified:\n- pom.xml: Replaced Jakarta EE WAR dependencies with Spring Boot JAR starters\n- Dockerfile: Updated build/run commands for Spring Boot fat JAR\n\nAdded:\n- src/main/java/com/example/order/OrderApplication.java: Spring Boot main class\n- src/main/java/com/example/order/entity/CustomerOrder.java: Migrated entity with @JsonIgnore\n- src/main/java/com/example/order/entity/LineItem.java: Migrated entity with @JsonIgnore\n- src/main/java/com/example/order/entity/LineItemKey.java: Migrated composite key class\n- src/main/java/com/example/order/entity/Part.java: Migrated entity with @JsonIgnore\n- src/main/java/com/example/order/entity/PartKey.java: Migrated composite key class\n- src/main/java/com/example/order/entity/Vendor.java: Migrated entity with @JsonIgnore\n- src/main/java/com/example/order/entity/VendorPart.java: Migrated entity with @JsonIgnore\n- src/main/java/com/example/order/service/OrderService.java: Spring @Service (replaces EJB RequestBean)\n- src/main/java/com/example/order/config/DataInitializer.java: Spring CommandLineRunner (replaces EJB ConfigBean)\n- src/main/java/com/example/order/controller/OrderController.java: Spring MVC + REST controller\n- src/main/resources/application.properties: Spring Boot configuration\n- src/main/resources/templates/order.html: Thymeleaf template (replaces JSF order.xhtml)\n- src/main/resources/templates/lineItem.html: Thymeleaf template (replaces JSF lineItem.xhtml)\n- smoke.py: 15 smoke tests covering all API and UI endpoints\n- CHANGELOG.md: Migration documentation\n\nRemoved:\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/order/ejb/ConfigBean.java: Replaced by DataInitializer\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/order/ejb/RequestBean.java: Replaced by OrderService\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/order/web/OrderManager.java: Replaced by OrderController\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/order/entity/*.java: Replaced by com.example.order.entity\n- src/main/liberty/config/server.xml: Open Liberty config (not needed)\n- src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/web.xml: Servlet config (not needed)\n- src/main/webapp/*.xhtml: JSF templates (replaced by Thymeleaf)\n- src/main/webapp/resources/css/default.css: Old CSS\n- src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml: JPA config (replaced by application.properties)\n```\n\n### Step-by-Step Log\n\n```\n[2026-03-16T23:55:00Z] [info] Analyzed project structure - Jakarta EE 10 web app\n[2026-03-16T23:58:00Z] [info] Updated pom.xml with Spring Boot 3.2.5 dependencies\n[2026-03-17T00:01:00Z] [info] Created entity classes in com.example.order.entity package\n[2026-03-17T00:02:00Z] [info] Created OrderService replacing EJB RequestBean\n[2026-03-17T00:03:00Z] [info] Created DataInitializer replacing EJB ConfigBean\n[2026-03-17T00:04:00Z] [info] Created OrderController with REST and Thymeleaf endpoints\n[2026-03-17T00:05:00Z] [info] Created application.properties for H2/JPA config\n[2026-03-17T00:06:00Z] [info] Created Thymeleaf templates replacing JSF views\n[2026-03-17T00:07:00Z] [info] Updated Dockerfile for Spring Boot\n[2026-03-17T00:08:00Z] [info] Created smoke.py with 15 tests\n[2026-03-17T00:10:00Z] [info] Initial Docker build successful, app starts\n[2026-03-17T00:10:30Z] [info] Initial tests: 10/15 passed\n[2026-03-17T00:12:00Z] [warning] JSON circular reference - added @JsonIgnore annotations\n[2026-03-17T00:15:00Z] [info] Rebuild successful, all 15/15 tests pass\n[2026-03-17T00:16:00Z] [info] Migration complete - documented in CHANGELOG.md\n```\n\n### Error Handling\n\n- **Error Summary:** 1 warning resolved during migration\n- **Critical Issues:** None - migration fully successful\n- **JSON Circular Reference (resolved):** Bidirectional JPA entity relationships caused infinite recursion in Jackson serialization. Fixed by adding `@JsonIgnore` annotations on back-reference sides.\n- **Manual Intervention Required:** None"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":533,"cache_read_input_tokens":145616,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":533,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1367},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"263c0197-604d-4139-b6dd-23a5ef8a48e5","uuid":"30ff0f97-899f-4d45-9325-e102ca6cfa8f"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":1716386,"duration_api_ms":1330230,"num_turns":132,"result":"The migration is complete. Here is the full report:\n\n---\n\n### Migration Summary\n\n- **Frameworks:** Jakarta EE 10 (Open Liberty) -> Spring Boot 3.2.5 (Embedded Tomcat)\n- **High-level actions:** Replaced EJB with Spring Services, JSF with Thymeleaf, Open Liberty with embedded Tomcat, added REST API, created 15 smoke tests\n- **Overall outcome:** Success - all 15 smoke tests pass, application builds, runs, and functions correctly\n\n### File Tree\n\n```\nModified:\n- pom.xml: Replaced Jakarta EE WAR dependencies with Spring Boot JAR starters\n- Dockerfile: Updated build/run commands for Spring Boot fat JAR\n\nAdded:\n- src/main/java/com/example/order/OrderApplication.java: Spring Boot main class\n- src/main/java/com/example/order/entity/CustomerOrder.java: Migrated entity with @JsonIgnore\n- src/main/java/com/example/order/entity/LineItem.java: Migrated entity with @JsonIgnore\n- src/main/java/com/example/order/entity/LineItemKey.java: Migrated composite key class\n- src/main/java/com/example/order/entity/Part.java: Migrated entity with @JsonIgnore\n- src/main/java/com/example/order/entity/PartKey.java: Migrated composite key class\n- src/main/java/com/example/order/entity/Vendor.java: Migrated entity with @JsonIgnore\n- src/main/java/com/example/order/entity/VendorPart.java: Migrated entity with @JsonIgnore\n- src/main/java/com/example/order/service/OrderService.java: Spring @Service (replaces EJB RequestBean)\n- src/main/java/com/example/order/config/DataInitializer.java: Spring CommandLineRunner (replaces EJB ConfigBean)\n- src/main/java/com/example/order/controller/OrderController.java: Spring MVC + REST controller\n- src/main/resources/application.properties: Spring Boot configuration\n- src/main/resources/templates/order.html: Thymeleaf template (replaces JSF order.xhtml)\n- src/main/resources/templates/lineItem.html: Thymeleaf template (replaces JSF lineItem.xhtml)\n- smoke.py: 15 smoke tests covering all API and UI endpoints\n- CHANGELOG.md: Migration documentation\n\nRemoved:\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/order/ejb/ConfigBean.java: Replaced by DataInitializer\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/order/ejb/RequestBean.java: Replaced by OrderService\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/order/web/OrderManager.java: Replaced by OrderController\n- src/main/java/jakarta/tutorial/order/entity/*.java: Replaced by com.example.order.entity\n- src/main/liberty/config/server.xml: Open Liberty config (not needed)\n- src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/web.xml: Servlet config (not needed)\n- src/main/webapp/*.xhtml: JSF templates (replaced by Thymeleaf)\n- src/main/webapp/resources/css/default.css: Old CSS\n- src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml: JPA config (replaced by application.properties)\n```\n\n### Step-by-Step Log\n\n```\n[2026-03-16T23:55:00Z] [info] Analyzed project structure - Jakarta EE 10 web app\n[2026-03-16T23:58:00Z] [info] Updated pom.xml with Spring Boot 3.2.5 dependencies\n[2026-03-17T00:01:00Z] [info] Created entity classes in com.example.order.entity package\n[2026-03-17T00:02:00Z] [info] Created OrderService replacing EJB RequestBean\n[2026-03-17T00:03:00Z] [info] Created DataInitializer replacing EJB ConfigBean\n[2026-03-17T00:04:00Z] [info] Created OrderController with REST and Thymeleaf endpoints\n[2026-03-17T00:05:00Z] [info] Created application.properties for H2/JPA config\n[2026-03-17T00:06:00Z] [info] Created Thymeleaf templates replacing JSF views\n[2026-03-17T00:07:00Z] [info] Updated Dockerfile for Spring Boot\n[2026-03-17T00:08:00Z] [info] Created smoke.py with 15 tests\n[2026-03-17T00:10:00Z] [info] Initial Docker build successful, app starts\n[2026-03-17T00:10:30Z] [info] Initial tests: 10/15 passed\n[2026-03-17T00:12:00Z] [warning] JSON circular reference - added @JsonIgnore annotations\n[2026-03-17T00:15:00Z] [info] Rebuild successful, all 15/15 tests pass\n[2026-03-17T00: